gerudok_observer

Interface GObservable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Element, ElementContainer, GeRuDocument, GeRuDocumentLink, GLink, GNode, GraphicElement, Model, Page, Project, Slot, TextElement, Workspace

    public interface GObservable
    Own implementation of Observable interface. Made to solve the problem with Java version of Observable being an abstract class and limiting the inheritance possiblities of Observable classes due to lack of multiple inheritance in the language.
    Author:
    Nikola Jovanovic
